      <li id="cite-4">FDA Warning Letter 674545-12192023 — Jeffrey W. Taub, M.D. / Children's Hospital of Michigan (Dec 19, 2023). <a href="https://www.fda.gov/inspections-compliance-enforcement-and-criminal-investigations/warning-letters/jeffrey-w-taub-mdchildrens-hospital-michigan-674545-12192023" rel="noopener">FDA.gov</a></li>
